  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic mini metroidvania Tiny Dangerous Dungeons returns in a completely rebuilt adventure! Guide Timmy the little treasure hunter through a new,  twice as large dungeon than in the original game! Discover new puzzles, new items, new secrets, and battle ferocious new bosses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NEW GRAPHICS AND MUSIC</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/b069a01200550f777f4f1fdae2197d0d.poster.avif?t=1741277959\" width=576 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/b069a01200550f777f4f1fdae2197d0d.webm?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/b069a01200550f777f4f1fdae2197d0d.mp4?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tiny Dangerous Dungeons has been completely rebuilt from scratch with better physics, new colorful graphics, and completely new soundtrack!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPANDED NEW DUNGEON </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/f483100972b315ea182c7276aba87a11.avif?t=1741277959\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras_big/f483100972b315ea182c7276aba87a11.avif?t=1741277959 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New rooms and secrets have been added to the dungeon, giving the players more reasons to explore and backtrack. The new dungeon is over twice as large than in the original game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEROCIOUS NEW BOSSES </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/23c1797c735e5adb1820e85be0c4cdc3.poster.avif?t=1741277959\" width=576 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/23c1797c735e5adb1820e85be0c4cdc3.webm?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/23c1797c735e5adb1820e85be0c4cdc3.mp4?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brand new boss fights have been added to the game, Seek out and fight against 5 new fearsome boss creatures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NEW SECRETS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/00cca312462dde66ec248e8bdc688458.apng?t=1741277959\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/00cca312462dde66ec248e8bdc688458.poster.avif?t=1741277959\" class=\"bb_img\" width=568 height=320 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret levels and mysterious new treasures have been hidden in the dungeon! What happens if you collect them all...?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic mini metroidvania Tiny Dangerous Dungeons returns in a completely rebuilt adventure! Guide Timmy the little treasure hunter through a new,  twice as large dungeon than in the original game! Discover new puzzles, new items, new secrets, and battle ferocious new bosses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NEW GRAPHICS AND MUSIC</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/b069a01200550f777f4f1fdae2197d0d.poster.avif?t=1741277959\" width=576 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/b069a01200550f777f4f1fdae2197d0d.webm?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/b069a01200550f777f4f1fdae2197d0d.mp4?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tiny Dangerous Dungeons has been completely rebuilt from scratch with better physics, new colorful graphics, and completely new soundtrack!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPANDED NEW DUNGEON </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/f483100972b315ea182c7276aba87a11.avif?t=1741277959\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras_big/f483100972b315ea182c7276aba87a11.avif?t=1741277959 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New rooms and secrets have been added to the dungeon, giving the players more reasons to explore and backtrack. The new dungeon is over twice as large than in the original game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEROCIOUS NEW BOSSES </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/23c1797c735e5adb1820e85be0c4cdc3.poster.avif?t=1741277959\" width=576 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/23c1797c735e5adb1820e85be0c4cdc3.webm?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/23c1797c735e5adb1820e85be0c4cdc3.mp4?t=1741277959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brand new boss fights have been added to the game, Seek out and fight against 5 new fearsome boss creatures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NEW SECRETS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/00cca312462dde66ec248e8bdc688458.apng?t=1741277959\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179810/extras/00cca312462dde66ec248e8bdc688458.poster.avif?t=1741277959\" class=\"bb_img\" width=568 height=320 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret levels and mysterious new treasures have been hidden in the dungeon! What happens if you collect them all...?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
